'''Jean Luc Mitana''' (yavutse 29 Nzeri 1983), ni [[Rwanda]] umunyarwanda no cinematographer .   Yabaye umukinnyi wa sinema muri firime zitandukanye zirimo ''Behind the Word'', ''Kai the Vendor'' and ''Strength in Fear''.  

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 29 Nzeri 1983 i [[Kigali]], mu [[Rwanda]].  

== Umwuga ==
Mu 2006, yinjiye mu itsinda rya Almond Tree Films Collective maze mu 2009, Mitana akora kuri filime izwi ku izina rya ''Maibobo'' iyobowe na Yves Montand Niyongabo kandi yerekanwe bwa mbere mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filimi rya Rotterdam mu 2010. Yatanzwe mu iserukiramuco rya Sinema Africano d'Asia e [[Amerika]] Latina ya 2011 i Milan, mu [[Butaliyani]].   Yayoboye ''SAA-IPO'' mu 2010. Yafatiwe amashusho i Kigali iterwa inkunga na Tribeca Film Institute. Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Tribeca 2011 hanyuma ryerekanwa mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya Durban 2011 na AfryKamera International Film Festival, Polonye mu 2011. Hanyuma muri 2014, yakoze muri documentaire ''Inyuma y'Isi'' iyobowe na Marie-Clementine Dusejambo. <ref name="Habyarimana" /> Muri 2014, yitabiriye impano ya Berlinale, aho yari muri Studio yo gutunganya.  

